==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Haver
<hw>Ha"ver</hw> <pr>(h⟦amac⟧"v⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos>
<ety>[Etymol. uncertain.]</ety> <def>To maunder; to talk foolishly; to
